train-reviews.name: Aljohn
train-reviews.review: We took the train from Paris to Amsterdam. We saw a lot of beautiful sceneries along the way. The cabin is clean and big. We were able to take a good rest. Just book the ticket though Klook as it's hassle free.

train-reviews.name: HAEBEEN
train-reviews.review: 헝가리 부다페스트에서 오스트리아 비엔나 넘어갔는데 너무 좋았어요💖💖 중간에 티켓 검사하니까 주의하시고! 그리고 번호 잘 확인해서 타주세요‼️사람들 서있는데 못 뚫고가요,, 중간에 외국인들이 다 도와주셔서 너무 고마웠고 한번 더 느끼는 여행이였어요🥰🥰

train-reviews.name: Harjyot Harbhajansingh
train-reviews.review: Swiss rail pass is a boom in case you are travelling to switzerland want to explore switzerland easily. This pass allows you to travel on any train, bus or ferry services. you also get discounted tickets to many attractions.

train-reviews.name: Jia Yi
train-reviews.review: With the ticket, it’s very convenient to travel everywhere. Don’t have to think of the cost and don’t have to queue to buy tickets. Can easily access to most of the public transport. Price is reasonable and it’s hassle free. Highly recommended 👍👍👍

train-reviews.name: LIANG YAN
train-reviews.review: 只要SHOW出手機畫面或印出紙本，給入口人員和查票人員看定位編號就可以了，很方便!SMART車廂就已經比高鐵舒服，有帶轉接頭的話座位還可以充電!搭配Klook的折扣真的很划算! 大推!

train-reviews.name: H M
train-reviews.review: Great travel, good scenery, convenient and easy to use the e-ticket, comfortable seats. Recommend everyone to take trains in Europe!

train-reviews.name: HSIAO JOU
train-reviews.review: 方便快速，但因為疫情的關係很早就提出退款申請然後也成功了，不知道為什麼票券沒被取消還一直提醒我們要出發了記得印票還要我填使用評價，實在有一點囧欸哈哈哈  不過要稱讚一下客服人員處理特別退票退款方案申請的速度很快也很積極，一般來說歐洲之星是不能退改的，但客路基於疫情原因願意協助退票真的很感謝，之後疫情結束要去歐洲玩的時候還是會使用這個方案訂票的！

train-reviews.name: ZHIYING
train-reviews.review: It’s the best decision to purchase the Swiss pass as we were travelling through Switzerland from Zurich down to zertmatt. We just jump up and down trains easily without much thought as it’s all covered. Save alot of time and effort to Q to get tix and pay for every tix highly highly recommend! Ps: you get awesome views on the train as you travel around, missing Switzerland very very much!

train-reviews.name: KAR LIP
train-reviews.review: Easy to use,  just show ur tickets to the train ticket counter and book for a sit for €5 from Santa Apolonia to Porto Camphana.  Even id book from Lisbon Orient they manage to change my ticket depart from Santa Apolonia because more convenient to this station from my hotel.
